## ğŸ“ˆ Performance Benchmarks

| Model | Speed (tokens/sec) | BLEU | Rouge-L | Memory (GB) |
|-------|------------------|------|---------|-------------|
| Llama3-8B | 42 | 24.8 | 46.1 | 2.1 |
| Qwen2.5-7B | 38 | 25.3 | 47.2 | 1.9 |
| **FasterDecodeMixer** | **89** | **24.7** | **46.9** | **1.1** |

*GPU: NVIDIA RTX 4090, Batch Size: 1*


